---
title: Balsamic-Glazed Venison Steak & Parsnip Mash with Sautéed Veggies & Sage Nuts
description: The sticky, sweet tartness of our balsamic glaze really gets the mouth-watering. Drizzled over tender seared venison steak and a side of sautéed veggies topped with toasted sage nuts, this completely luxe dish will make the average dinner feel like a special occasion.
